  9→//!
 10→//! ```text
 11→//! .forge/skills/
 12→//! ├── rust-conventions/
 13→//! │   └── SKILL.md      # Rust-specific guidance
 14→//! ├── testing-strategy/
 15→//! │   └── SKILL.md      # Testing approach
 16→//! └── api-design/
 17→//!     └── SKILL.md      # REST/GraphQL patterns
 18→//! ```
 19→//!
 20→//! # Phase Integration
 21→//!
 22→//! Phases can reference skills in their JSON definition:
 23→//!
 24→//! ```json
 25→//! {
 26→//!   "number": "03",
 27→//!   "name": "API implementation",
 28→//!   "skills": ["rust-conventions", "api-design"],
 29→//!   "promise": "API COMPLETE"
 30→//! }
 31→//! ```
 32→//!
 33→//! Skills are injected into the phase prompt between the specification and task sections.
